events.blurb: Augustine of Canterbury arrives in Britian.
events.description:
Augustine of Canterbury arrived in 597. He focused on Kent, so it
probably didn't impact northern Scotland till much later.
events.source:
The Editors of Encyclopaedia Britannica.
